<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently, the only way to set multiple request parameters in Zend_Http_Client is by successive calls to setParameterPost() and setParameterGet(). This is inconvenient when multiple parameters are required.</p>

<p>Please add setParametersPost() and setParametersGet() (note the plural) to simplify this process.</p>

